          <p class="text-sm">Complete redesign in Framer before next investor round. Used Relume to plan sitemap (5 minutes, mapped all sections). Exported wireframes to Framer. Built custom landing page: smooth scroll animations, investor testimonials section, pricing page (future pricing), demo video integration, founder bio with LinkedIn/VC background. Total build time: 3 hours (faster with Relume planning). Custom domain: saasapp.com (not .wixsite). PageSpeed score: 98 (was 67). Load time: 0.8s (was 4.2s). Looked like a real company, not a template.</p>
