            <li><strong>Month 3:</strong> Beta expanded to 1,200 users. Framer site added: user testimonials section, case studies ("how Company X reduced churn 47%"), live demo integration. Mobile traffic 73%, mobile experience perfect (Framer mobile-first by default). Conversions mobile vs desktop: 73% vs 64%. Month 3 revenue: $12K MRR (up from $0 pre-funding). Hired third employee (customer success). Planning Series A raise. Website will get messaging overhaul before next investor meetings. Framer makes updates trivial.</li>
