            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border-[2px] border-gray-200 p-5">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-red-500 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">âœ•</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-black text-gray-900">"Subdomains are fine for MVP"</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">Truth: Pre-launch used .wixsite subdomain. Waitlist: 127 emails in 2 months. Bought custom domain ($15): same site, week 1: 89 emails, week 2: 143 emails. 2x improvement. Subdomain says "hobby." Custom domain says "business." Trust difference = massive. Investors notice subdomains. Customers notice subdomains. $15/month is table stakes for any business.</p>
