          <p class="text-sm">
            <strong>Quick reality check:</strong> Your website is your first investor meeting. Before they see your product, before they hear your pitch, they visit your site. If it looks like a cheap template, they assume you cut corners everywhere. Framer + Relume gives you professional results without dev team. Durable gets you fast but looks cheap. For fundraising: choose quality over speed. $15/month difference = $250,000 investment gained or lost.
          </p>
